proposal:
Hello Frog CEO community! 🐸

As you all know, the world of meme tokens is a competitive one. But what if we told you that we have some tools that could give your favorite amphibian a leg up in the race? 🏁

We're not here to play games, we're here to help you create them. With our B2B tools, you can take Frog CEO from just a meme token to a full-fledged ecosystem. 🌐

1. 🔄 DEX (UNI FACTORY)
   - Hop into the DeFi world with your own DEX based on Uniswap V2.
   - Set your own commission from 0.00% to 20%.

2. 🎰 Lottery
   - Create a blockchain-based lottery and earn up to 30% commission.
   - Supported Blockchains: ETH, BSC, Polygon - all the places a frog can hop to!

3. 🪙 Wallet
   - Create a multicurrency crypto wallet for all your Frog CEO tokens and more.

4. 🌾 Farming
   - Create ERC20 Staking & Yield Farming. Attract investment by offering rewards.

5. 🗳 DAO
   - Governance and proposals for your Frog CEO token. Let the community have a say!

6. 🌉 CrossChain
   - Create an EVM compatible blockchain bridge. Frogs are known for their jumping ability, after all!

7. 🚀 IDOFactory - Launchpad
   - Launchpad solution for IDO pools and token locking.

And the best part? It's all B2B, so you're not just playing, you're creating. If you're interested, let's hop to it! 🐸

Check out our demos: https://t.me/onoutdemos
